posts.post_content: Would like to work on this team set after buying a Chesbro. Let me know if you have any of the commons, Keelers, or Chases and are willing to sell/trade. Thank you.

Thought you might like to see the complete set (minus Doyle of course)....  I don't have any extras now, but am upgrading as I see them...

Beautiful set!!!  It is under Tcdyess in the PSA registry if you want a peek....

Enjoy!!

Tim
